text: Matteo Bisiani is an Italian archer. He was born on 2 August 1976. Bisiani competed at the 1996 Summer Olympics and at the 2000 Summer Olympics.Matteo BisianiMatteo BISIANI == References == Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Italian archers Category:Olympic silver medalists for Italy Category:Olympic bronze medalists for Italy Category:Sportspeople from Friuli- Venezia Giulia
